# Service-only secrets for search-service.
#
# Only search-service's code reads these (ClaudeSummarizer/GeminiSummarizer —
# verified via grep, no other service references them). Kept out of the
# shared root .env so core-api/notification-service/auth-service/worker-service
# never load a paid API key they don't use — see .ai/memory/conventions.jsonl
# (2026-07-05, "env-centralization-tradeoff-analysis-and-env-example-rewrite").
#
# Copy to apps/search-service/.env.secrets (gitignored) and fill in real values.
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=
GEMINI_API_KEY=
